{% block availability %}
We've integrated all RUS 12 tables with the exception of six totals tables
containing aggregated versions of values present in other tables. RUS data
is only available through 2021 because this is the last year a FOIA request
was submitted. Future updates of this data will require additional FOIA
requests. If you are interesting in supporting this please contact
pudl@catalyst.coop.

